## 2. About StudyPebbles

StudyPebbles is a technology consulting and delivery team focused on building modern, scalable digital products.

### Core Areas of Expertise

StudyPebbles specializes in:

* UX and UI engineering
* Web application development
* Backend systems using Java and Spring Boot
* WordPress-based solutions for startups and small businesses
* Cloud-ready application architecture
* API-driven systems

StudyPebbles focuses on **clean architecture, maintainable systems, and production-quality engineering**.

---

## 3. StudyPEBBLES Application

### Purpose

The demo application exists to:

* demonstrate backend architecture
* showcase clean domain separation
* illustrate API-driven design
* demonstrate how AI can be embedded safely into enterprise systems

The demo is **not a production system**.

---

### What the Demo Application Can Do

The demo application supports:

* client onboarding simulation
* portfolio management simulation
* demonstration of REST APIs
* demonstration of AI-based knowledge assistance
* sample data creation for demonstration purposes

All data in the demo is **non-production and simulated**.

---

### What the Demo Application Cannot Do

The demo application does not:

* process real financial transactions
* connect to live systems
* store real customer data
* integrate with third-party services
* perform background jobs
* execute automated actions through AI

---

## 4. Demo Application Limitations

The demo application is intentionally limited.

Known limitations include:

* in-memory or local database usage
* limited validation
* simplified workflows
* no authentication or authorization
* no real document storage
* no external integrations

These limitations are by design.

---

## 5. Demo Usage Guidance (Instructional Only)

### Uploading Documents

Document upload in the demo is a **simulated workflow**.

Users can:

* access the upload section from the UI
* select a document
* submit the form

The upload is intended only to demonstrate UI and API flow, not real document processing.

---

### Using the Demo

Users can:

* navigate between demo screens
* trigger sample workflows
* observe API responses
* understand system structure

The AI assistant only explains how these features work conceptually.

The AI does not perform actions.

